00:32:52,419 --> 00:32:54,594
Dearly beloved, wonder
not if the world hate you.

485
00:32:54,595 --> 00:32:57,693
We know that we have passed from death
to life because we love the brethren.

486
00:32:57,693 --> 00:32:59,569
He that loveth not
abideth in death.

487
00:32:59,569 --> 00:33:01,417
Whosoever hateth his
brother is a murderer.

488
00:33:01,418 --> 00:33:04,706
And you know that no murderer hath
eternal life abiding in himself.

489
00:33:04,707 --> 00:33:07,208
In this we have known
the charity of God.

490
00:33:30,886 --> 00:33:32,570
And in God's house...

491
00:33:36,269 --> 00:33:39,502
Goodness and mercy all my
life shall surely follow me...

492
00:33:39,503 --> 00:33:41,623
and in God's house forevermore...

493
00:33:42,249 --> 00:33:44,776
Oh, my! I think I'm going to die.

494
00:33:47,550 --> 00:33:49,425
They say Willy can
climb a wall of glass.

495
00:33:49,426 --> 00:33:51,546
If anyone can do it,
Clean Willy can.

496
00:34:27,104 --> 00:34:30,039
Oh, my! I think I'm going to die.

497
00:34:35,258 --> 00:34:36,944
Where is he?

498
00:35:35,201 --> 00:35:37,321
Good heavens! He's
in a right bad state.

499
00:35:37,321 --> 00:35:38,653
