538
00:39:21,267 --> 00:39:24,746
Hmph! Fancy Dan and Stunning
Bill. Wasn't my fight, was it?

539
00:39:24,746 --> 00:39:26,432
Put a sovereign on Bill.

540
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:30,346
Well, he won! I've a
quid to show for it.

541
00:39:38,012 --> 00:39:40,269
I'll take another walk round.
See you later.

